data.description: Large home with beautiful high-end finishes throughout. Granite countertops; LVT floors; Modern colors and design. Thekitchen is gorgeous and has a walk in pantry, island seating and stainless appliances. Master bedroom is a spacious retreatwith a large walk-in closet, and a fabulous master bathroom with a large walk-in, tiled shower. Centrally located in the heart ofGrand Junction. Close to Hospitals, schools, college, shopping and more.
